  "description": "Tonight’s twenty minute recipe is an explosion of fresh flavours and one that you’ll be coming back to time and time again. Stir fried pork is coated in a glossy marinate of ginger, honey, soy sauce, ketjap manis and fresh lime juice and served over a warm and nourishing rice salad. For added texture and flavour, finish off with chopped peanuts, spring a onions and a good squeeze of lime.",
